## Executive Summary

### ‚úÖ Strengths
- **Clean component architecture** ‚Äî Logical separation into `home/` and `layout/` directories with single-responsibility components
- **TypeScript usage** ‚Äî Proper type definitions for [ExperienceItem](file:///Users/asiermunoz/Documents/personal-portfolio/src/types/experience.d.ts#1-9), [ExperienceProps](file:///Users/asiermunoz/Documents/personal-portfolio/src/types/experience.d.ts#10-14), and [ProjectCardProps](file:///Users/asiermunoz/Documents/personal-portfolio/src/types/project.d.ts#1-8) in [.d.ts](file:///Users/asiermunoz/Documents/personal-portfolio/src/types/project.d.ts) files
- **Basic responsive breakpoint** ‚Äî A `768px` media query exists in most CSS files for mobile adaptation
- **Semantic HTML elements** ‚Äî Uses `<nav>`, `<footer>`, `<main>`, `<section>`, and `<article>` where appropriate
- **Accessibility basics** ‚Äî Footer social links have `aria-label` attributes; external links use `rel="noopener noreferrer"`

### üî¥ Critical Weaknesses
- **No CSS custom properties (design tokens)** ‚Äî All colors, spacing, and fonts are hardcoded across 8 separate CSS files, making theming/maintenance very difficult
- **Duplicate and conflicting CSS rules** ‚Äî `body` styles defined in both [App.css](file:///Users/asiermunoz/Documents/personal-portfolio/src/styles/App.css) and [Home.css](file:///Users/asiermunoz/Documents/personal-portfolio/src/styles/Home.css); `.tech-tag` declared twice in [ProjectCard.css](file:///Users/asiermunoz/Documents/personal-portfolio/src/styles/ProjectCard.css)
- **No tablet breakpoint** ‚Äî Only a single `768px` breakpoint exists; layouts break between 769px‚Äì1024px
- **Footer breaks on mobile** ‚Äî Horizontal `flex` layout with no wrap causes overflow on small screens
- **Missing meta tags** ‚Äî No `<meta name="description">`, no Open Graph tags, poor `<title>` text
- **Console.log in production code** ‚Äî [ProjectCard.tsx](file:///Users/asiermunoz/Documents/personal-portfolio/src/components/home/ProjectCard.tsx) has a debug `console.log` statement
- **Global `*` selector with `font-weight: 650`** ‚Äî Aggressively sets all elements to semi-bold, overriding natural weights
- **Unused `React` import** ‚Äî [ProjectCard.tsx](file:///Users/asiermunoz/Documents/personal-portfolio/src/components/home/ProjectCard.tsx) imports `React` unnecessarily (React 19 doesn't need it for JSX)
- **No focus styles** ‚Äî Navbar buttons and links have no `:focus-visible` styles, harming keyboard navigation
- **Image assets not optimized** ‚Äî [WeatherApp.png](file:///Users/asiermunoz/Documents/personal-portfolio/src/assets/WeatherApp.png) is 1.2 MB; [playpal.png](file:///Users/asiermunoz/Documents/personal-portfolio/src/assets/playpal.png) is 2.2 MB (unused but bundled)

