## Refactored Code

All changes below are applied directly to the codebase. Key improvements:

### 1. Global Design Tokens & Reset (`App.css`)

**Before:**
```css
body {
    background-color: #222;
    font-family: system-ui;
    color: #fff;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 100vh;
}
```

**After:**
```css
:root {
  /* ‚Äî Color Palette ‚Äî */
  --color-bg:          #1a1a2e;
  --color-bg-surface:  #16213e;
  --color-bg-card:     #0f3460;
  --color-accent:      #e94560;
  --color-accent-hover:#ff6b81;
  --color-gold:        #ffd34e;
  --color-text:        #eaeaea;
  --color-text-muted:  #b0b0b0;
  --color-border:      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);

  /* ‚Äî Typography ‚Äî */
  --font-primary: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
  --font-mono:    'JetBrains Mono', monospace;

  /* ‚Äî Spacing scale (rem) ‚Äî */
  --space-xs:  0.25rem;
  --space-sm:  0.5rem;
  --space-md:  1rem;
  --space-lg:  1.5rem;
  --space-xl:  2rem;
  --space-2xl: 3rem;
  --space-3xl: 4rem;

  /* ‚Äî Borders & Shadows ‚Äî */
  --radius-sm: 6px;
  --radius-md: 12px;
  --radius-lg: 20px;
  --shadow-card: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  --shadow-hover: 0 12px 40px rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.15);

  /* ‚Äî Transitions ‚Äî */
  --transition-fast: 0.2s ease;
  --transition-base: 0.3s ease;
}
```
> Adds a centralized design system. Changing a single variable now updates the entire site.

### 2. SEO & Performance (`index.html`)

**Before:**
```html
<title>personal-portfolio</title>
<link rel="icon" href="/src/assets/icono.png" />
```

**After:**
```html
<title>Asier Mu√±oz | Software Engineer Portfolio</title>
<meta name="description" content="..." />
<meta property="og:title" content="..." />
<link rel="icon" href="/icono.png" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
```
> Proper SEO tags, preconnected fonts for faster LCP, favicon moved to `public/`.

### 3. Navbar Focus & Accessibility

**Before:** No `:focus-visible` styles, global `* { font-weight: 650 }`.

**After:**
```css
.nav-button:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid var(--color-accent);
  outline-offset: 2px;
}
```
> Keyboard users can now see focus indicators. Removed the overly aggressive global `*` selector.

### 4. Footer Responsive Fix

**Before:** Footer had `display: flex` with no wrapping ‚Äî content overflowed on mobile.

**After:**
```css
