## Best Practices Checklist for Future Features

| # | Suggestion | Details |
|:--|:-----------|:--------|
| 1 | **Dark/Light Mode Toggle** | Leverage the CSS custom properties to swap `--color-bg`, `--color-text`, etc. using a `data-theme` attribute on `<html>`. Store preference in `localStorage`. |
| 2 | **Optimize Largest Contentful Paint (LCP)** | Convert PNGs to WebP/AVIF, add `loading="lazy"` and `width`/`height` to images, preload critical hero content. Target LCP < 2.5s. |
| 3 | **Add Page Transitions / Scroll Animations** | Use `IntersectionObserver` for reveal-on-scroll animations. Consider `framer-motion` for route transitions. |
| 4 | **Extract Data to JSON/TS Constants** | Move project data and experience items to `src/data/projects.ts` and `src/data/experience.ts`. Makes future CMS integration trivial. |
| 5 | **Add `prefers-reduced-motion` Support** | Wrap all CSS `transition` and `animation` in `@media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference)` to respect user accessibility settings. |
